# Eventora — Skills & Coding Conventions

Panduan teknis dan pola kode yang HARUS diikuti saat mengerjakan setiap task di project Eventora.

---

## 1. File & Naming Conventions

### File Naming
| Type | Convention | Example |
|------|-----------|---------|
| React Component | PascalCase | `TemplateShowcase.tsx` |
| Page Route | lowercase folder | `app/tema/page.tsx` |
| Utility/Helper | camelCase | `themeRegistry.ts` |
| Type Definition | camelCase | `invitation.ts` |
| CSS Module | camelCase | `hero.module.css` |
| Constant Data | camelCase | `pricingData.ts` |

### Folder Rules
- Satu component per file — jangan gabung banyak export component dalam satu file
- Komponen shared/reusable taruh di `src/components/ui/`
- Komponen spesifik halaman taruh di folder sesuai: `landing/`, `dashboard/`, `themes/`
- Data statis (arrays, objek pricing, testimonial) taruh di `src/data/` sebagai file terpisah
- TypeScript types taruh di `src/types/`

---

## 2. Component Architecture

### Server vs Client Components

```
DEFAULT = Server Component (tanpa "use client")
Gunakan Client Component HANYA jika perlu:
  - useState, useEffect, useRef
  - Event handlers (onClick, onChange)
  - Framer Motion animations
  - Browser APIs (localStorage, window)
```

**Pola yang benar:**
```tsx
// ✅ Server Component — page.tsx
import { ClientHero } from "@/components/landing/Hero";
export default function Home() {
  return <ClientHero />;
}

// ✅ Client Component — Hero.tsx
"use client";
import { motion } from "framer-motion";
export function Hero() { ... }
```

### Component Props Pattern
```tsx
// ✅ Selalu definisikan interface untuk props
interface FeatureCardProps {
  title: string;
  description: string;
  icon: React.ComponentType<{ className?: string }>;
  delay?: number;
}

export function FeatureCard({ title, description, icon: Icon, delay = 0 }: FeatureCardProps) {
  // ...
}
```

### Data Separation Pattern
```tsx
// ✅ BENAR — data di file terpisah
// src/data/features.ts
export const features = [
  { title: "...", description: "...", icon: "infinity" },
];

// src/components/landing/Features.tsx
import { features } from "@/data/features";
```

