## 3. Styling Conventions (Tailwind CSS v4)

### Theme Token Usage
```tsx
// ✅ Gunakan token dari design system
className="bg-background text-foreground border-border"
className="bg-primary text-white hover:bg-primary-dark"
className="text-muted"

// ❌ JANGAN hardcode warna
className="bg-[#059669]"  // ← Hindari, kecuali di dalam theme component
```

### Responsive Pattern
```tsx
// ✅ Mobile-first ordering
className="text-2xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl"
className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3"
className="px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-8"
```

### Spacing Pattern
```tsx
// ✅ Section spacing konsisten
// Setiap section landing page:
className="py-16 md:py-24"  // vertical padding
// Container di dalam section:
className="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6"
```

### Card Pattern
```tsx
// ✅ Standard card styling
className="bg-surface rounded-2xl border border-border p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300"
```

### Tailwind v4 Theming (`@theme inline`)
```css
/* globals.css — Cara mendaftarkan custom color ke Tailwind v4 */
@theme inline {
  --color-primary: var(--primary);
  --color-primary-dark: var(--primary-dark);
  --color-primary-light: var(--primary-light);
  --color-primary-50: var(--primary-50);
  --color-accent-rose: var(--accent-rose);
  --color-surface: var(--surface);
  --color-muted: var(--muted);
}
```

