## 5. Membuat Theme Undangan Baru (Step-by-Step)

### Langkah 1: Buat file component
```
src/components/themes/NamaTheme.tsx
```

### Langkah 2: Gunakan struktur dasar ini
```tsx
"use client";

import { motion } from "framer-motion";
import type { InvitationData } from "@/types/invitation";

interface ThemeProps {
  data: InvitationData;
}

export function NamaTheme({ data }: ThemeProps) {
  const {
    groom_name, bride_name, event_date, event_location,
    event_map_url, gallery_images, music_url, message,
    groom_father, groom_mother, bride_father, bride_mother,
    love_story, bank_accounts,
  } = data;

  return (
    <div className="min-h-screen" style={{ /* theme colors */ }}>
      {/* 1. COVER SECTION — fullscreen, "Buka Undangan" button */}
      {/* 2. COUPLE SECTION — names, photos */}
      {/* 3. EVENT DETAILS — date, time, venue */}
      {/* 4. COUNTDOWN — live timer */}
      {/* 5. LOVE STORY (optional) */}
      {/* 6. GALLERY — photos grid */}
      {/* 7. RSVP FORM */}
      {/* 8. GUEST WISHES — message feed */}
      {/* 9. GIFT REGISTRY — bank accounts */}
      {/* 10. MAPS — Google Maps embed */}
      {/* 11. FOOTER — "Powered by Eventora" */}
    </div>
  );
}
```

### Langkah 3: Daftarkan di theme registry
```tsx
// src/lib/themeRegistry.ts
import dynamic from "next/dynamic";

export const themeRegistry: Record<string, {
  name: string;
  component: React.ComponentType<any>;
  category: string;
  colors: { primary: string; bg: string };
}> = {
  "emerald-garden": {
    name: "Emerald Garden",
    component: dynamic(() => import("@/components/themes/EmeraldGarden").then(m => m.EmeraldGarden)),
    category: "wedding",
    colors: { primary: "#059669", bg: "#F0FDF4" },
  },
  // ... tambahkan tema baru di sini
};
```

### Langkah 4: Update `[slug]/page.tsx`
```tsx
import { themeRegistry } from "@/lib/themeRegistry";

export default async function InvitationPage({ params }) {
  const { slug } = await params;
  const invitation = await fetchInvitation(slug); // dari Supabase
  const theme = themeRegistry[invitation.theme_id];
  if (!theme) return <div>Theme not found</div>;
  const ThemeComponent = theme.component;
  return <ThemeComponent data={invitation} />;
}
```

### Rules untuk Theme Component:
1. **Warna HARUS di-hardcode** dalam theme (bukan pakai token global) — setiap tema punya palet sendiri
2. **Mobile-first** — undangan 95% dibuka di HP, pastikan tampilan di 375px sempurna
3. **Selalu gunakan `motion`** untuk reveal animations di setiap section
4. **Font** — load via `next/font/google` di theme itu sendiri atau di layout
5. **Cover** harus fullscreen (`min-h-screen`) dengan tombol "Buka Undangan"
6. **RSVP Form** harus functional — submit ke API `/api/rsvp`

