```bash
# Branch naming
feature/landing-hero
feature/theme-emerald-garden
fix/pricing-responsive
refactor/color-system

# Commit message format (Bahasa Inggris)
feat: add testimonials carousel section
fix: pricing card overflow on mobile
style: update hero gradient colors
refactor: extract theme base component
```
